java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.EventListener, javax.swing.Action
public class CmdSaveGIF
extends CmdSaveGraphics

Cmd to save a diagram as a GIF image in a supplied OutputStream. Requires the Acme.JPM.Encoders.GifEncoder class. Operates on the diagram in the current editor. Code loosely adapted from CmdPrint.

Author:
Steve Poole, stevep@wrq.com

TRANSPARENT_BG_COLOR

public static final int TRANSPARENT_BG_COLOR
Used as background color in image and set transparent. Chosen because it's unlikely to be selected by the user, and leaves the diagram readable if viewed without transparency.
